snippet.title: Garfield Double Dares (1985) - Apple II MiSTer FPGA Core - GARFATHON #3
snippet.description:
Now I'm tackling "Garfield Double Dares", another educational Apple II game. This one appears to be pretty much Scrabble, with the betting and all. (I've never played Scrabble.) Originally streamed on http://twitch.tv/srmxy


(Played on MiSTer FPGA, Apple II core.)
